---
title: Meatball Wraps with Wedges and Yoghurt Dip
description: If you’re looking for a speedy recipe with plenty of flavour, these delicious meatball wraps make a great quick-fix dinner. As we’re always looking for clever ways to cut down time in the kitchen, our pork suppliers have perfectly seasoned the sausage meat so that you don’t have to! When everything is ready to go, place all the ingredients in the middle of your table and get everyone to build their own wraps exactly how they want them. Fast food at its finest!
